{{Quote|Shut down all the garbage mashers on the Detention Level!|Luke Skywalker|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 4">[[Star Wars (1977) 4|''Star Wars'' (1977) 4]]</ref>}}
'''Deck 5''', also called '''Level 5''', '''Detention Level''', or '''Prison Level''', was the level of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star I]] where [[Detention Block AA-23/Legends|Detention Block AA-23]] and [[Garbage Compactor 3263827]] were located. [[Corridor Six]] was on located on this level. It was destroyed during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

